@startuml security_flow_ZH
!theme plain
title AuthGate — 安全检测与告警流程

actor 客户端
participant "SecurityMiddleware\n(中间件)" as MW
participant "RateTracker\n(速率追踪)" as Rate
participant "ScanRequest\n(模式扫描)" as Scan
database "13 组攻击模式\n(~90 条正则)" as Patterns
participant "SecurityLogFunc\n(回调函数)" as LogFunc
participant "CloudWatch\n(aws/cloudwatch.go)" as CW
participant "CloudMonitor\n(aliyun/cloudmonitor.go)" as CM
participant "SNS / PagerDuty\n(告警通知)" as Alarm

== 每个请求必经 ==
客户端 -> MW : HTTP 请求

== 第 1 层: 速率检测 ==
MW -> Rate : Record(IP, Path)
Rate -> Rate : 滑动窗口 60s\n每秒桶粒度

note over Rate
  5 级阈值:
  ├─ RATE_ELEVATED_IP_PATH (低)    ≥10 次/60s 同一IP→同一路径
  ├─ RATE_BURST_PATH (中)          ≥1000 次/60s 同一路径
  ├─ RATE_BURST_IP_PATH (高)       ≥100 次/60s 同一IP→同一路径
  ├─ RATE_BURST_IP (高)            ≥500 次/60s 同一IP
  └─ RATE_STORM (严重)             ≥5000 次/60s 全局
end note

Rate --> MW : 速率告警 (如有)

== 第 2 层: 攻击模式扫描 ==
MW -> MW : io.ReadAll(r.Body) → 缓冲请求体
MW -> Scan : ScanRequest(body, path, query, headers)

Scan -> Patterns : 扫描 4 个源 × 13 组规则

note over Patterns
  严重 (25 条正则):
  ├─ SQL_INJECTION     — UNION, DROP, OR '1'='1', SLEEP(), xp_cmdshell
  └─ COMMAND_INJECTION — ;cat, |ls, `id`, $(whoami), &&wget

  高危 (46 条正则):
  ├─ XSS               — <script>, onerror=, javascript:, eval()
  ├─ PATH_TRAVERSAL    — ../../, /etc/passwd, /proc/self/
  ├─ SSRF              — 169.254.169.254, metadata.google.internal
  ├─ FILE_INCLUSION    — php://, /wp-admin/, .ini?%00
  ├─ NOSQL_INJECTION   — $gt, $where, $regex
  ├─ SENSITIVE_FILE    — .env, .git/, config.json, id_rsa, Dockerfile
  └─ XML_ATTACK        — <!ENTITY ... SYSTEM, <![CDATA[

  中危 (15 条正则):
  ├─ DIR_BRUTE_FORCE   — /admin, /wp-admin, /actuator/env, /jenkins
  ├─ CROSS_ORIGIN      — CSRF token 模式
  └─ HEADER_INJECTION  — \r\nLocation:, \r\nSet-Cookie:

  低危 (2 条正则):
  ├─ SCANNER_UA        — sqlmap, nikto, nessus, burp, zap, nmap
  └─ EXCESSIVE_PARAMS  — &key=value 模式
end note

Scan --> MW : 模式匹配结果 (如有)

== 第 3 层: 合并与路由 ==
MW -> MW : all = 速率告警 + 模式匹配

alt len(all) > 0
    MW -> LogFunc : SecurityLogFunc(method, path, srcIP, ua, all)

    group AWS Lambda 环境
        LogFunc -> CW : LogSecurityEvent() → JSON → CloudWatch Logs
        note over CW
          结构化 JSON 日志:
          {
            "event": "security.threat",
            "severity": "CRITICAL",
            "category": "SQL_INJECTION",
            "match_count": 3,
            "path": "/auth/login",
            "source_ip": "1.2.3.4",
            "user_agent": "sqlmap/1.0",
            "matches": [...]
          }
        end note

        LogFunc -> CW : EmitSecurityMetric() → EMF 指标
        note over CW
          AuthGate/Security.ThreatDetected
          维度: Category, Severity
        end note
    end

    group 阿里云 FC 环境
        LogFunc -> CM : LogSecurityEvent() → JSON → SLS
    end
end

== 第 4 层: 告警通知 ==
group CloudWatch 告警
    CW -> CW : Metric Filter\n{ $.severity = "CRITICAL" }
    CW -> CW : Alarm: count >= 1 per 1 min
    CW -> Alarm : SNS → PagerDuty / Slack / 邮件
    note over Alarm
      严重 → PagerDuty (立即电话通知)
      高危 → Slack #security-alerts
      SQL注入 → 安全团队邮件
      速率风暴 → PagerDuty + 钉钉
    end note
end

group CloudMonitor 告警 (SLS)
    CM -> CM : 告警查询\nseverity: CRITICAL | SELECT COUNT(*)
    CM -> CM : 触发: cnt >= 1
    CM -> Alarm : 短信 / 电话 / 飞书 / 钉钉
end

== 请求永不阻断 ==
MW -> MW : next(w, r)
note over MW : 纯检测模式\n阻断在 WAF / API Gateway 层

@enduml
